{"tid":741693,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"凡事太上心 痛在自己心","createTime":"2018-07-14T01:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T12:31:51.000Z","uid":146869,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d638370636b2bee8074b02f260804c70ca88d909","tid":741693,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:46:17.000Z","msg":"明明第一日識好多計傾咩都講一餐<br />\n而你每次回覆都成百字咁濟 之後仲要主動拎我contact<br />\n點解要做埋啲令人誤會既行為 令我呢個毒撚覺得你想approach我 對我有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個日之後我開始留意你既一切 因為我覺得我地好有機會 所以想了解你多啲<br />\n自從交換完wts 就好似變咗另一個人咁<br />\n遲覆都算 覆親都幾個字hea撚到爆 online緊都可以一直唔覆人<br />\n會唔會係覺得純傾計太無癮？咁我咪主動踏出第一步約佢出街 點撚知你又係俾啲無意義既答案嚟拖鳩我<br />\n<br />\n追一個人追到咁撚攰同灰 我都係趁早離場唔好令自己愈踩愈深算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能個晚你純粹想搵個人陪你傾計解悶 所以你先會表現到咁積極 一切都係毒撚ff得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多撚謝你俾咗個假希望我<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/eh53ykt_XqY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Feh53ykt_XqY&d=bJxTfcuo2CwFfVN18A5NBGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=706e12bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/eh53ykt_XqY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c702ecc5fa3a24fadfc18dda3fa9ee8e6fa3e952","tid":741693,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:49:06.000Z","msg":"入樹仁悔終生，ou恆大更稱心"},{"pid":"99c38851da13764c40c4aa6b64986bb89caf12d3","tid":741693,"uid":146869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c702ecc5fa3a24fadfc18dda3fa9ee8e6fa3e952","tid":741693,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:49:06.000Z","msg":"入樹仁悔終生，ou恆大更稱心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"含撚啦垃圾<br />\nBtw呢排唔係俾警犬拉撚咗？"},{"pid":"21d9ac81838a1fd772863c6bd82468897ef5de2a","tid":741693,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99c38851da13764c40c4aa6b64986bb89caf12d3","tid":741693,"